metadata.title: The Chabas Network
metadata.author: Thomas Lebée
metadata.description: Data for the analysis of François Chabas' correspondence. It was used for the paper "Analysing the epistolary network of a self-isolated egyptologist: François Chabas" presentend to the Digital Orientalist Twitter Conference 2020 (#DOsTC2020).
